processing_metadata.description: Official Virginia DMV processing rules and validation requirements

global_rules.code_system: Information needed - research plate type code system
global_rules.character_restrictions: Uses both O and 0 - O with letters, 0 with numbers; State uses both letter 'O' and number '0'

omit: vertical/diagonal with different font or color
stacked_characters.position: Y - Omit printed vertical or diagonal characters with different font or color.; Y - Vertical characters must be verified as seen.; Y - Omit printed vertical or diagonal characters with different font or color, such as VET.
stacked_characters.notes: INCLUDE: ID, ZE, TR (e.g., VA-730591TR), RS in symbol (VA-FD48917, VA-RSVESTA), FD from Fire Fighter logo. OMIT vertical or diagonal characters with different font or color. Letter O is rounder than number 0.; Extracted from 9 plate types with character modifications

processing_metadata.character_modifications: Allows letter O on personalized plates
